com.morpheus.sdk.infrastructure

Class ServerInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.morpheus.sdk.infrastructure.ServerInterface

  • public class ServerInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    A Model representation of a Morpheus Server Interface It is used by GSON Decoder to convert JSON of the following structure into a java based Object. 
        "interface": {
        "active": true,
        "class": "com.morpheus.ComputeServerInterface",
        "dhcp": true,
        "id": 10,
        "ipAddress": "10.100.54.2",
        "ipSubnet": null,
        "ipv6Address": null,
        "ipv6Subnet": null,
        "name": "eth0",
        "network": null,
        "networkPosition": null,
        "primaryInterface": true,
        "publicIpAddress": null,
        "publicIpv6Address": null,
        "server": {
          "class": "com.morpheus.ComputeServer",
          "id": 22
        }
      }
